The following is a step-by-step guide:
(1). Download our "Bliss by Zonefirst" application in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Start the application and register a new account (if you have already registered, please log in);
(3). Open the LST device and connect with the "Bliss by Zonefirst" application;
(4). Important information: You can use ZonefirstApp to rename the device. Therefore, if the thermostat is named "Home Kitchen", then after discovering the device in step 9, Echo will get the same name.
(5). Download the Amazon "Alexa" application from the Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with the "Alexa" application;
(6). Search "Zonefirst" in the Alexa Skills directory;
(7). Click to enable the "Zonefirst" skill, then enter your account username, password
(8). Talk to Echo "" Alexa, discover the device. ". Wait until Echo answers" Discovery completed ";
(9). Now complete all settings. Try talking to Echo to control your device
(10). Alexa, set Home Kitchen to [off,auto, heat, cool] mode
Alexa, set Home bedroom to 77 degrees.
